        <h2 class="r-fit-text"> Architecture </h2>
        <ul>
        	<li> <b>Sardine: </b> the main library.
        	<li> <b>Fishery: </b> the code interpreter.
        	<ul>
        		<li> <b>Fishery Web:</b> The embedded code editor.
        	</ul>
        	<li> <b>Ziffers-Python:</b> standalone plugin for the Ziffers notation.
        </ul>

